        "en-x-generated": "<p>A soil remediation expert is an independent expert recognised by the managing official of the Public Waste Agency of Flanders (OVAM). There are two types of soil remediation experts.</p><ul><li>A <strong>type 1</strong> recognised soil remediation expert is recognised for carrying out <strong>exploratory soil investigations </strong>and drawing up <strong>reports </strong>in the context of <strong>soil movement</strong>.</li><li>A recognised type <strong>2</strong> soil remediation expert may perform <strong>all tasks</strong> assigned to a soil remediation expert under the Soil Decree (and its implementing decrees).</li></ul><p>Consult the <a href=\"https://ovam.vlaanderen.be/lijstbsd\">list of soil remediation experts</a> on the website of the Public Waste Agency of Flanders (OVAM).</p>",
